'''本杰明·姆瓦鲁瓦里'''（{{lang-en|'''Benjamin Mwaruwari'''}}，{{bd|1978年|8月13日|catidx=Mwaruwari, Benjani}}），通常稱'''本贾尼'''（'''Benjani'''）是一名已退役[[辛巴威|辛巴威]]職業足球員。

==生平==
麥華路禾尼在[[布拉瓦約|布拉瓦約]]出生，青少年時期在國內聯賽打滾，於1999年出國投效[[南非|南非]]球會{{tsl|en|Jomo Cosmos||約莫宇宙}}（Jomo Cosmos），逐漸打出名堂，期間獲外借到[[瑞士|瑞士]][[苏黎世草蜢足球俱乐部|草蜢]]。得到[[居伊·魯|居伊·魯]]的賞識，麥華路禾尼於2001年轉投[[法甲|法甲]][[欧塞尔足球俱乐部|歐塞爾]]，最初發展順利，但當[[積基斯·辛天尼|積基斯·辛天尼]]在2005年接手任教後失去正選席位。

2006年1月麥華路禾尼以410萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]加盟由[[哈里·雷德克纳普|哈利·列納]]帶領的[[英超|英超]]球隊[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|朴茨茅斯]]，其後揭發這單交易涉及貪污。在為球隊上陣超過70場，兩年後轉投[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]，初步作價為387萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽約兩年半<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7221987.stm |title=Benjani completes Man City move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-05 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309172228/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7221987.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期間被受傷患困擾，2010年1月被借用到[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]直到球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/8492573.stm |title=Benjani makes loan move from Man City to Sunderland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-02 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122061923/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/8492573.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，季後約滿被曼城放棄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/8728341.stm |title=Petrov, Sylvinho and Benjani to leave Manchester City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-06-08 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125022827/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/8728341.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年8月27日麥華路禾尼加盟[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布莱克本流浪者]]，由於有膝傷舊患陰影，僅獲一年合約，但有優先續約一年權<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackburn_rovers/8928984.stm |title=Blackburn Rovers sign striker Benjani Mwaruwari |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-27 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |archive-date=2010-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100829195605/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/blackburn_rovers/8928984.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣21場僅射入3球，包括主場3-1擊敗[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]個人[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9331205.stm |title=Blackburn 3-1 Liverpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-05 |accessdate=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2019-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109040235/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9331205.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季後約滿的麥華路禾尼一度遭布力般流浪放棄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13793152.stm |title=Several Africans on the free transfer list in England |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-06-16 |accessdate=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2011-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110620044314/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13793152.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但於6月22日獲球會提供1年新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13878934.stm |title=Blackburn Rovers striker Benjani to sign new deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-06-22 |accessdate=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2011-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811234142/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13878934.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。惟麥華路禾尼拒絕接受，於2011年8月13日以[[自由球員|自由身]]重返[[英冠|英冠]]效力[[樸茨茅夫足球會|樸茨茅夫]]，簽約一年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14516645.stm |title=Benjani makes Portsmouth return |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-13 |accessdate=2011-08-14 |archive-date=2011-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925073954/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14516645.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

